text: When I get online search you again, your gray portrait let me down.
There is hesitation in my heart. I just want to hide my love.
Love is a vine that grows in my heart. I lost myself, I miss you.
I know some day I will say my love. Say your love. I’ll be lonely without you.
Just one more try. How I wish we could be free to love. I wanna pray.
Pray for the true love lighten my life. Love lighten my life.
Going through the labyrinth I see. You are like sweet morning light.
Your smile as the rainbow after rain. Take me as yours, take my life.
You are music always on my mind. Flowers come out love arrive.
Melodies for you will never end. Though life is brief, love is long. Though life is brief, love is long.
I know your love. I know your love. I know you are the one I only love. I know you are the one I only love.
I’m standing here. I’m standing here. You are the true love lighten my life. Love lighten my life.
Going through the labyrinth I see. You are like sweet morning light. Your smile as the rainbow after rain.
Take me as yours, take my life.
